          <h2 data-toc-text="Identify Spell">Changes to the Identify Spell</h2>
            <p>Discovering a magic item and learning its use(s) is no easy task.  A short/long rest with the item in your possession may no longer reveal how a magic item works.  You may need to rely on experimentation and the Identify spell (changes below).</p>

            <p><b>Identify:</b>
            <p>Identify casting time is now 1 hour.</p>
              <p>During this time you become perfectly still and enter a trance like state. At the end of the hour you will gleam information on how the magics in the item(s) are arranged, including its schools, and a vauge idea on how the item might be used.  Some experimenting may be needed to test your theory depending on the power level of the magic item.</p>
              <p>Learning what spells are affecting a <i>creature</i> takes the RAW 1 minute.</p>

